            <!-- how it works section -->
            <div class="row justify-content-center" id="howitworks">
                <div class="col-lg-10 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 text-center">
                <h4>How It Works</h4>
                <div class="row">
                    <ul>
                        <li> 1. Commit to donating just $5 a month</li>
                        <li>2. Every month we'll feature three causes to support. You have five days to select 1 or more to donate your $5 to.</li>
                        <li> 3. If you forget to make a selection, the cause with least donations will be chosen for you by default.
                    </ul>
